Synth Controlling UGens


the UGens listed here can affect a node's state from within the synth, 
they can free or pause nodes, for example.


Done
 FreeSelf
 PauseSelf
FreeSelfWhenDone
PauseSelfWhenDone
 Pause
 Free


UGens with a doneAction

EnvGen
 Linen
Line
XLine
 DetectSilence
 Duty
 TDuty


See [UGen-doneActions] for more detail on done actions.

 

 